{
  "stem": "11000.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From Westerbork, we were sent to Theresienstadt, the four of us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My parents, my sister, and I together.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] We arrive in Theresienstadt, and we, again, were assigned different jobs.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My sister, I remember, worked at the farm.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They had farms outside the camp, and I think my mother was at some kind of an industry called [?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Glimmer ?], which they-- the women had to work, and it had something to do with the defense industry.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I really don't know exactly what it was.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was assigned, again, to the carpenter shop, which wasn't too hard of work.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The unique thing in-- the unique thing in Theresienstadt was we got paid.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I got paid for my work with money.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We had are own money.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You probably have seen it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It's printed, and it says Theresienstadt and who the [GERMAN] was and so forth.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The only problem with the money was you were unable to buy anything with it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They did have a store with items showing in a window.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then I learned that this was all done because [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I believe Theresienstadt was helped by the Swiss Red Cross and-- to put on a show to make believe that this is the way it really was, which it wasn't.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Whenever we got the inspection from the Swiss Cross, when the people came, then everything was put to show and make believe that, look how good we treat the Jews.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I remember the little children had to run up to the commander when he walked with his inspectors from Switzerland through camp and make believe that, you know, do you have any candy for us today and so forth?",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was Theresienstadt.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't have any bad experience there.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
